============================================================
SCOPE NOTES
============================================================

The Apache-2.0 license on templates and scripts was chosen for
compatibility with most upstream Solana program licenses (the largest
ecosystem repos use Apache-2.0 or MIT). If you adapt a template into
an upstream program with a different license, the resulting derivative
takes the upstream's license; the template itself remains Apache-2.0
in this repository.

Verify upstream licenses before redistributing template-derived test
code at scale.
